2838          //--------------------------------------------------
2839          // Description  :
2840          //ucBorderPixel        bit5~3 shadow/border width or 3D button thickness in pixel unit:0~7 1~8 pixel.
2841          //                            bit2~0 shadow/border height  in line unit:0~7 1~8 line.
2842          //
2843          //ucBorderColor      bit7~4 shadow/border/3D button left-top/botton border color
2844          //                           bit3~0 shadow/border/3D button right-botton/top border color
2845          //
2846          //ucWinFuncControl: bit7: blend  0:disable, 1:enable
2847          //                            bit6: gradient 0:disable, 1:enable
2848          //                            bit5: gradient direction  0:H, 1:V
2849          //                            bit4: shadow/border/3D button 0:disable, 1:enable
2850          //                            bit3~1:0~3: shadow type 1~4,  4~5: 3D button1~2, 6:reserved, 7:border.
2851          //
